  Kinetic (Delta T^0):                   1.091964637069376         29.7139           685.22          2866.95
  Delta V^Pauli Coulomb:                -0.661689830984566        -18.0055          -415.22         -1737.27
  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.209961424632211         -5.7133          -131.75          -551.25
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.045337329136366          1.2337            28.45           119.03
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.028345963537448         -0.7713           -17.79           -74.42
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.237304747051517          6.4574           148.91           623.04
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

